#: index.docbook:744
msgid "Building and Installing kdm"
msgstr "Generando e instalando kdm:"

#: index.docbook:746
msgid ""
"&kdm; is part of the KDE project. The various component parts of the KDE "
"project are broken into sections, called packages. &kdm; is part of the "
"package called kdebase. You can get KDE source code from various Linux and "
"BSD distribution CDs, or by download from <ulink "
"url=\"http://www.kde.org\">www.kde.org</ulink> or its mirrors. If you have "
"an out-of-date source code tree, you can use one of the KDE cvsup servers to "
"bring it up-to-date whilst using minimal network bandwidth."
msgstr ""
"&kdm; es parte del proyecto KDE. Los diversos componentes del proyecto KDE "
"están divididos en secciones, denominados paquetes. &kdm; es parte del "
"paquete denominado kdebase. Usted puede obtener el código fuente de KDE de "
"diversas distribuciones Linux y BSD en CDs, o descargando desde <ulink "
"url=\"http://www.kde.org\">www.kde.org</ulink> o cualquiera de sus "
"réplicas. Si dispone de un árbol fuente obsoleto, puede utilizar uno de "
"los servidores cvsup de KDE para actualizarlo utilzando poco ancho de banda."

#: index.docbook:755
msgid ""
"Before building kdebase, you must have built and installed (in this order) "
"version 2 of the qt library and the KDE packages kde-qt-addon, kdesupport "
"and kdelibs."
msgstr ""
"Antes de generar, debe haver creado e instalado (en este orden) la versión "
"2 de la biblioteca qt y de los paquetes KDE kde-qt-addon, kdesupport y "
"kdelibs."

#: index.docbook:759
msgid ""
"In order to build any of the above, you must already have the X Window "
"System installed, together with a C++ compiler and the GNU configuration "
"tools <application>configure</application>, "
"<application>automake</application> and <application>autoconf</application>."
msgstr ""
"Para poder crear todo lo anterior, debe tener instalado ya el Sistema de "
"Ventanas X, junto con un compilador C++ compiler y las herramientas GNU de "
"configuración <application>configure</application>, "
"<application>automake</application> y <application>autoconf</application>."

#: index.docbook:764
msgid ""
"If the last few paragraphs seemed like a foreign language, then either you "
"have strayed into an Inappropriate Area of this handbook, or you are about "
"to undergo a Great Learning Experience."
msgstr ""
"Si los últimos parrafos le parecen escritos en arameo, entonces o bien se "
"ha perdido en un Area Inapropiada de este manual, o está a punto de vivir "
"una Gran Experiencia de Aprendizaje."

#: index.docbook:768
msgid ""
"If you managed to satisfy all of the prerequisites, you are unlikely to have "
"any problems with building and installing kdebase. &kdm; is installed in "
"your \"<filename>$KDEDIR/bin</filename>\" directory."
msgstr ""
"Si se las ha arreglado para satisfacer todos los prerequisitos, "
"probablemente no tenga problemas generando e instalando kdebase. &kdm; se "
"instalará en su directorio \"<filename>$KDEDIR/bin</filename>\"."

#: index.docbook:772
